        "title": "Core Concept Interrelation",
        "content": "Regions, Availability Zones, and AWS services work together to provide a resilient and scalable cloud environment:\n\n*   Services are deployed within Regions and can span multiple Availability Zones for high availability.\n*   Understanding the relationship between these concepts is essential for designing robust cloud solutions.\n*   As mentioned in 'Core Concepts of AWS Explained', proper selection of Regions and AZs directly impacts application performance and resilience."
